          <li style="padding: 0.5rem 0;">✓ Access to all frameworks</li>
          <li style="padding: 0.5rem 0;">✓ Generate unlimited prompts</li>
          <li style="padding: 0.5rem 0;">✓ <strong>Save unlimited prompts</strong></li>
          <li style="padding: 0.5rem 0;">✓ <strong>Export prompts as files</strong></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align: center; padding: 2rem; background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px;">
      <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #7f8c8d;">For testing purposes, you can upgrade to premium using the button below.</p>
      <form method="POST" action="/admin/make-premium">
        <button type="submit" class="btn" style="font-size: 1.125rem; padding: 0.75rem 2rem;">Upgrade to Premium (Test)</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  `}
